#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the task performance chart, we can analyze deeply each subtask or task "
"with the same indexes as for the project performance view."
msgstr ""
"En el gràfic de compliment de la tasca, podem analitzar en profunditat cada "
"subtasca o tasca amb els mateixos índexs que per a la vista Realització del "
"projecte."

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is really useful in a long and complicated project."
msgstr "Això és realment útil en un projecte llarg i complicat."

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left window, you can choose every single sub-task as well as an "
"entire task, then on the right window will appear in the corresponding chart."
msgstr ""
"A la finestra esquerra, podreu triar cada subtasca individual i una tasca "
"completa, després a la finestra dreta apareixerà en el gràfic corresponent."

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "where:"
msgstr "On:"

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "BCWS means Budgeted Cost Work Scheduled,"
msgstr "BCWS vol dir el cost pressupostat de la feina planificada,"

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "BCWP means Budgeted Cost Work Performed,"
msgstr "BCWP vol dir el cost pressupostat de la feina realitzada,"

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "ACWP means Actual Cost Work Performed."
msgstr "ACWP vol dir el cost real de la feina realitzada."

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "All these are considered as effort in hours and costs."
msgstr "Tots aquests són considerats com a esforç en hores i costos."

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "PI are the Performance Indexes, where:"
msgstr "PI són els índexs de compliment, on:"

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "CPI is the Cost Performance Index,"
msgstr "CPI és l'índex de compliment del cost,"

#. Tag: para
#: taskperformanceview.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "SPI is the Schedule Performance Index."
msgstr "SPI és l'índex de compliment de la planificació."
